# Description

Implement the `status` command to show comprehensive daemon status, device connection, battery level, feature states, and current mode.

## CLI Interface

```
surface-dial status          # Human-readable status
surface-dial status --json   # Machine-readable status
surface-dial status --watch  # Continuous status updates (1/sec)
```

